                        <provenance>The manuscript was either acquired by <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3182ContiRo">Carlo Conti Rossini</persName> 
                            during his stay in <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC2991Eritre">Eritrea</placeName>
                            (<date notBefore="1899" notAfter="1903">1899–1903</date>) or sent to him after his return to Europe. It is possible that 
                            it was copied by <persName role="scribe" cert="low" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3182ContiRo"><certainty locus="value" match="@role"/>Carlo Conti Rossini</persName>  himself.</provenance>
                        <acquisition>The manuscript passed into the possession of the library in <date when="1950">1950</date>, following Conti Rossini’s death in <date when="1949">1949</date> 
                            (see <ref target="https://www.menestrel.fr/?-Roma-&amp;lang=fr#845">Menestrel</ref>).</acquisition>
